LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "FEATURE: Pirates boss level can now be completed by hitting other ships with bouncing CannonBalls.\nBUGFIX: Arena no longer casts shadows on bridges.\nBUGFIX: Bridges are no longer created when moving portals during a level unless needed.\nCHANGE: SciFi AlienPlanet > Virus03 now launches in an arc instead of straight line.\nCHANGE: Pirates > CannonBall now bounces on platform.", "created_date": 1725412909, "id": "7475591059209076", "version": "0.40.2.0", "version_code": 598, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "5477835475651321", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "7475591059209076"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "2493148167513843"}]}, "change_log": "FEATURE: SciFi Wifi (SciFi Campaign #2) levels 1-5 are now completely rewritten.\nFEATURE: Added skybox to SciFi Wifi.\nBUGFIX: Bridges are now correctly raised before level starts.\nBUGFIX: Portal changes now correctly lower/raise bridges during level.\nCHANGE: More level difficulty rating adjustments.\nCHANGE: Bob animations now starts going up then bobs downward.\nCHANGE: SciFi > PenroseTriangle now rotates after teleporting.\nCHANGE: SciFi > Earth is now a low-poly model.", "created_date": 1722286827, "id": "7267340980034086", "version": "0.40.1.0", "version_code": 597, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "b